title: ATK Archives Pack 02 - 250 Models
description:
I have included samples, the first picture of each set for all 575 sets. To save space all pictures have been reduced in resolution. Otherwise the sample folder would have been over 100 MB in size, just a little bit crazy. 

Some of the samples have been re-named with their enclosing folder name because some file do not follow the standard ATK naming scheme and would have been much harder to locate correctly.

Please make the samples folder your priority download to make it easier and faster for others to download

Enjoy!!
